  15 Dec 2011; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  synaptiks-0.8.0.ebuild:
  Removing --single-version-externally-managed, thx arfrever

  15 Dec 2011; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> synaptiks-0.8.0.ebuild:
  Use python 2, fixes bug #387533 thanks floppym. Use appropiate eclass for
  test, fixes bug #394575. Fix SRC_URI, uses now mirror, thanks repoman.

  04 Nov 2011; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  synaptiks-0.8.0.ebuild:
  Use kde4-base.eclass to automatically handle handbook useflag, bug 387421

  18 Oct 2011; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  synaptiks-0.8.0.ebuild:
  Does not work with python-3, bug 387533

